      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like a loop. i wake up, i remember they're gone, and i just feel this crushing weight in my chest all over again. it's not even sadness anymore, it's just... nothingness. like i'm already dead but just forgot to stop breathing. how am i supposed to keep doing this every single day? it feels so exhausting.",
