      "content": "it just feels like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. people keep saying things will get better or to talk to someone, but that doesn't change the fact that the person who made my life worth living isn't here. the future i planned is just... gone. there is no \"getting through\" this, there is just more of this same pain. why is there even a point to trying when the only thing waiting for me is more emptiness?",
